Package: lmspline
Title: Fit a linear spline for piecewise regression.
Version: 0.0.0.9000
Authors@R: as.person("Creagh Briercliffe <creagh@stat.ubc.ca> [aut, cre]")
Description: Given a number of knots, n, this function will place n knots
    at evenly spaced quantiles of the data, and fit a linear regression spline.
    Returned is a list with the fitted coefficients and knots used.
Depends:
    R (>= 3.1.1)
License: CCO
LazyData: true
